control

Class Control

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.Control
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlLink

    public class Control
extends java.lang.Object
implements ControlLink
    Control implements a controlLink to manage any given data structure that stores the photoalbum's state. Also stores certain information about the current user while they are logged in.
    Author:
    Joe
